      "text": "> Introducing an open, standards-based, decentralised vision of the metaverse for the open Web, built entirely on Matrix… without cryptocurrencies, NFTs or walled gardens."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "b4bfa660763f5c91",
      "text": "Aren't walled gardens just one of the benefits of our wiki? Would we lose that with Third Room? [https://matrix.to/#/!ORfrUEFeWFcHAMLFLr:matrix.org/$166430712348ksHLb:dreyeck.freedombox.rocks?via=matrix.org&via=matrix.allmende.io&via=chat.weho.st matrix]"
